Package: betfaiR
Type: Package
Title: R client for Betfair's API
Version: 0.6
Date: 2015-07-11
Author: Thomas Heslop
Maintainer: Thomas Heslop <t_heslop@hotmail.co.uk>
Description: R client for the Betfair Exchange API.  Retrieve data about markets,
    competitions, events, runners, prices, etc.  Place orders (bets), replace,
    update, and cancel orders.  Retrieve data about your account, available funds,
    statement, etc.    
License: MIT
LazyData: TRUE
Imports:
    httr,
    jsonlite,
    plyr,
    stringr,
    ggplot2
Suggests:
    testthat
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
